                Hey there! Welcome to the <strong>Digital Garden</strong>, where <strong>You</strong> get to grow your own flower in this vibrant virtual space! 🌼🎉
                All you need is a <strong>GitHub account</strong> and a sprinkle of imagination. 🦣🌺
            </p>

            <h4 class="description-title">Our Epic Vision & Goals 🚀🐦‍🔥</h4>
            <p class="description">
                We’re on a quest to build <strong>the most epic</strong> virtual garden ever, blooming with flowers from <strong>amazing people</strong> like you! 🪻🌈
                Each person can plant just <strong>one flower</strong>, making every single bloom extra special. So dive in, plant your flower, and help us create a garden that’s truly out of this world! 📝🦕
            </p>

            <h4 class="description-title">Get Involved and Shine! 💐🐙</h4>
            <p class="description">
                Ready to jump in? 🌱
