                <strong>Note:</strong> Since this is <strong>still a demo</strong>, you might spot a few bugs or hiccups. 🐞✨
                Thanks for being <strong>awesome</strong> and helping us grow. Happy planting!🧑‍🌾🐛🪴
            </p>
